🔐 4. Encryption System
Purpose
To ensure that employee time‑tracking data cannot be accessed or modified by unauthorized users.

Features
Symmetric encryption for log files

Secure key storage

Separate decryptor tool for admin use

Protection against tampering

Security Considerations
Passwords should be hashed

Encryption keys must not be hardcoded

Logs should be validated before decryption

